pipeline ingest_cities for data

  does:
    Fetch a CSV of US cities and load it into the warehouse,
    validating that the LatD column has no null values.

  source http_csv
    url "https://people.sc.fsu.edu/~jburkardt/data/csv/cities.csv"

  sink sqlite
    connection "warehouse"
    table "cities"

  through ingest_and_validate

  bind:
    column = "LatD"
